        "text": "If governance processes and architectures can take into account collective concerns by design at any level (at least potentially), then our starting point is to recognize that we can't start this process at a disaggregated level. The larger architectures, dynamics and processes must be understood on their own terms. It's time for a closer look at *macropatterns* based on a commoning embody living practices, attitudes and ethics at larger scales."
